(35, 1, '2024-12-01 06:20:04', '2024-12-17 20:59:10', 'Công ty TNHH ZIGExN VeNtura', 16, NULL, 'Fresher IT Comtor (Japanese N2)_HN/HCM_V000009\r\nMức lương : 500 - 1,000 USD\r\nĐịa điểm: Hà Nội, Hồ Chí Minh\r\nKinh nghiệm dưới 1 năm', 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/RntGdRsebAlnJ33sT7yS1734494350.webp', '<h2>Chi tiết tin tuyển dụng</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n C&ocirc;ng nghệ th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>M&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>About ZIGExN</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Get excited to create Life Media Platforms from Vietnam to the World!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At&nbsp;<strong>ZIGExN VeNtura</strong>, we&rsquo;re part of a larger vision driven by&nbsp;<strong>ZIGExN Co., Ltd.,</strong>&nbsp;a leading life media platform company in Japan. Our parent company is renowned for offering over&nbsp;<strong>40 services</strong>&nbsp;in various life event domains such as&nbsp;<strong>jobs, housing, cars, and travel</strong>. With accolades like the&nbsp;<strong>Japan Technology Fast 50 award</strong>&nbsp;(Deloitte, 2015) and recognition as a&nbsp;<strong>Great Place to Work</strong>&nbsp;in Japan, we&rsquo;re now taking an exciting journey to expand our impact globally.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At&nbsp;<strong>ZIGExN VeNtura</strong>, we specialize in&nbsp;<strong>software development</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>Internet services</strong>, creating multi-product software based on a&nbsp;<strong>life media platform</strong>. Our talented engineers work across&nbsp;<strong>3 offices</strong>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<strong>Ho Chi Minh</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Hanoi</strong>, and&nbsp;<strong>Da Nang</strong>, collaborating to build innovative solutions that make a difference.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your Role</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a member of the development team, YouYou will work closely as a supporter for the Bridge Software Engineer (BrSE). Your responsibilities include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Supporting the translation of specification documents and facilitating communication between Japanese and Vietnamese teams.</li>\r\n	<li>Support in the management of project schedules to ensure timely progress.</li>\r\n	<li>Support in the management of product quality through activities such as user testing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This role serves as a vital link to enhance collaboration and ensure the project&#39;s success across cultural and linguistic boundaries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your Mission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Communicate and discuss</strong>&nbsp;directly with the development team to clarify requirements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cooperate</strong>&nbsp;with the project leader to&nbsp;<strong>solve issues of progress/quality and suggest new test methods&nbsp;</strong>to improve project productivity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Y&ecirc;u cầu ứng vi&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your Profile</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are looking for a talented individual who thrives in a dynamic, collaborative, and fast-paced environment. The ideal candidate should have:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your career path is targeted to be an advanced IT human resource such as BrSE and PM in the future.</li>\r\n	<li>You have a strong desire to learn Japanese, project management, technical knowledge, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Good at writing, reading in Japanese. (Equivalent to N2 or upper).</li>\r\n	<li>Good communication skills &amp; be careful to work in detail.</li>\r\n	<li>Eager to learn technical skills and &ldquo;can-do&rdquo; attitude in a technology environment.</li>\r\n	<li>Proactive and high sense of responsibility, willing to cooperate with team members and be a good team player to achieve the goal.</li>\r\n	<li>Basic English in reading &amp; writing is definitely a plus.</li>\r\n	<li>Job opportunities for freshers who graduated from the university with Japanese as the main subject. The one who gets the basic IT knowledge is priority.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Quyền lợi</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Offer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At&nbsp;<strong>ZIGExN VeNtura</strong>, we believe in fostering an environment where our employees can thrive both professionally and personally. Here are some of the benefits and perks you can look forward to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Salary: Negotiable based on your Japanese skills.</li>\r\n	<li>85% salary on 2 months of probation.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>13th-month salary</strong>&nbsp;and performance-based bonuses.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>15-18 days</strong>&nbsp;of paid leave per year for employees with over 1 year of service.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>MacBook/ Laptop</strong>&nbsp;provided to meet your work requirements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Language support programs</strong>&nbsp;for learning&nbsp;<strong>Japanese</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>English</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Performance appraisal</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>salary review</strong>&nbsp;twice a year.</li>\r\n	<li>Full gross salary payment for&nbsp;<strong>compulsory insurance</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Awards</strong>&nbsp;for outstanding performance on a quarterly and yearly basis.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why ZIGExN?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Be Recognized &ndash; Training &amp; Development Environment:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Skill-up training programs</strong>&nbsp;to help you continuously grow.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Technical mentors</strong>&nbsp;to guide and support your development.</li>\r\n	<li>Regular feedback and guidance from&nbsp;<strong>Leaders/Managers</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>6-month performance evaluations</strong>&nbsp;tied to career advancement.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Salary reviews</strong>&nbsp;twice per year to reward your development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Positive Team Environment with Lots of Fun &amp; Chills:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Free snacks and drinks</strong>: Fresh milk, coffee, tea, yogurt, Red Bulls, etc.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Exciting events</strong>: Birthday celebrations, pizza parties, and cultural festivities like Christmas, Halloween, and Full Moon Festival.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sports activities</strong>: Join football, table tennis, swimming, and badminton clubs.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Quarterly events</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>year-end parties</strong>, and an annual&nbsp;<strong>company trip</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>We Care About Your Health:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive&nbsp;<strong>Bao Viet Premium Healthcare packages</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Annual health checkups</strong>&nbsp;to ensure you stay in great shape.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Địa điểm l&agrave;m việc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&agrave; Nội: 6 Nguyễn Ho&agrave;ng, Mỹ Đ&igrave;nh 2, Nam Từ Li&ecirc;m</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Hồ Ch&iacute; Minh: 131 X&ocirc; Viết Nghệ Tĩnh, Phường 17, B&igrave;nh Thạnh</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Thời gian l&agrave;m việc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thứ 2 - Thứ 6 (từ 08:00 đến 17:00)</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>C&aacute;ch thức ứng tuyển</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ứng vi&ecirc;n nộp hồ sơ trực tuyến bằng c&aacute;ch bấm&nbsp;ngay dưới đ&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hạn nộp hồ sơ: 25/12/2024</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.topcv.vn/cong-ty/cong-ty-tnhh-zigexn-ventura/1036.html\">C&ocirc;ng ty TNHH ZIGExN VeNtura</a></p>', 1),
(36, 1, '2024-12-01 06:27:11', '2024-12-01 06:27:11', 'CÔNG TY TNHH HG.GLOBAL', 16, 1, 'Sales Leader/ Trưởng Nhóm Kinh Doanh (Biết Tiếng Anh Hoặc Tiếng Nhật) - Thu Nhập 15-30 Triệu\r\nMức lương: 15 - 30 triệu\r\nĐịa điểm: Hà Nội\r\nKinh nghiệm 1 năm', 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/6pcsZebzC2lHf4LpWTvx1733059631.webp', '<h2>Chi tiết tin tuyển dụng</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n: Sales Điện/Điện tử/Viễn th&ocirc;ng kh&aacute;c&nbsp;Telesales&nbsp;Thương mại điện tử&nbsp;B&aacute;n lẻ - H&agrave;ng ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng - FMCG&nbsp;Viễn th&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>M&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Thực hiện c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng việc được ph&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng bởi quản l&yacute; trực tiếp.</li>\r\n	<li>Tranning nh&acirc;n sự mới.</li>\r\n	<li>Thực hiện c&aacute;c nhiệm vụ kh&aacute;c theo y&ecirc;u cầu của cấp tr&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n	<li>L&agrave;m việc nh&oacute;m v&agrave; hỗ trợ đồng nghiệp.</li>\r\n	<li>Tu&acirc;n thủ c&aacute;c quy định v&agrave; quy tr&igrave;nh của c&ocirc;ng ty.</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; tinh thần tr&aacute;ch nhiệm cao trong c&ocirc;ng việc.</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; khả năng l&agrave;m việc độc lập v&agrave; l&agrave;m việc nh&oacute;m.</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; khả năng th&iacute;ch nghi nhanh với m&ocirc;i trường l&agrave;m việc mới.</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; khả năng giải quyết vấn đề v&agrave; ra quyết định.</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; khả năng giao tiếp tốt v&agrave; l&agrave;m việc hiệu quả.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Y&ecirc;u cầu ứng vi&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tr&ecirc;n 1 năm kinh nghiệm ở vị tr&iacute; Sale Leader.</li>\r\n	<li>Tốt nghiệp trung cấp, cao đẳng, đại học chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh li&ecirc;n quan.</li>\r\n	<li>Giao tiếp tr&ocirc;i chảy tiếng Anh hoặc tiếng Nhật (tr&igrave;nh độ từ N3 hoặc Toeic từ 650 v&agrave; tương đương trở l&ecirc;n)</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; khả năng l&agrave;m việc độc lập v&agrave; l&agrave;m việc nh&oacute;m, c&oacute; tinh thần tr&aacute;ch nhiệm trong c&ocirc;ng việc.</li>\r\n	<li>C